%h1 Chibrary

%p
  Chibrary ("shy-brary") provides free, highly-readable public mailing list
  archives. If you run a list, we'd probably be happy to archive it. (More
  <a href="/about">about</a> the site.)

.lists
  <h2>All Lists</h2>
  %ul
    - @lists.each do |list|
      %li= "<a href=\"/#{list.slug}\">#{(list.title_name)}</a>"

.snippets
  <h2>Recent Messages</h2>
  %ul
    - @snippets.each do |snippet|
      %li
        %a.subject{ href: snippet['url'] }= subject(snippet['subject'])
        %span.excerpt= h snippet[:excerpt]
